        <mxCell id="h5end" value="" style="shape=mxgraph.bpmn.shape;perimeter=mxPerimeter.ellipsePerimeter;symbol=terminate;outline=end;isEnd=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" vertex="1" parent="pool2">
          <mxGeometry x="670" y="100" width="25" height="25" as="geometry"/>
